1. Preprocessing:

gcc -E main.c -o main.i // -E option to stop after preprocessing step
with extension .i

2. Compiler:

gcc -S main.i -o main.s // -S to stop after compiling, extension .s

3. Assembling

gcc -c main.s -o main.o // Produce object code, exteeension .o
-c option stops before linking

4. Linking:

gcc main.o -o main //Produces final binary after linking
